## 4. Business Role of Square in the Platform

Square supports the **paid membership layer** of the platform.

The application contains these membership plan codes:

| Internal Plan Code | Tier | Billing Cycle | Intended Role |
|---|---|---|---|
| `basic_free` | basic | free | no Square billing |
| `standard_monthly` | standard | monthly | recurring paid plan |
| `standard_annual` | standard | annual | recurring paid plan |
| `premium_monthly` | premium | monthly | recurring paid plan |
| `premium_annual` | premium | annual | recurring paid plan |

### Important rule

Only paid plans should be sold through Square. The application already enforces this by rejecting plans with billing cycle `free` from Square checkout.

