| `standard_monthly` | Standard plan, monthly variation |
| `standard_annual` | Standard plan, annual variation |
| `premium_monthly` | Premium plan, monthly variation |
| `premium_annual` | Premium plan, annual variation |

### Mapping rule

The internal plan code should remain the application source of truth. Square IDs should only be stored as external references.

