| `audit_logs` | admin/system governance trail |

## 17.2 User state updates expected

The user document should reflect the current platform truth after sync.

### Typical fields updated

- `membershipPlanCode`
- `membershipTier`
- `membershipStatus`
- `billingCycle`
- `squareSubscriptionId`
- `squareCustomerId`
- `squareSubscriptionStatus`
- `lastPaymentStatus`
- `membershipExpiresAt`
- `updatedAt`

## 17.3 Entitlement rule

After lifecycle sync completes, the rest of the platform should be able to determine access solely from the user document and related subscription/grant records.

